--[[
    Auto Bounty
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------
    - Accepts ONLY bounties whose rewards include "Trait Shards" (trait rerolls)
    - Declines bounties that do NOT give trait shards
    - Runs ONE bounty active at a time
    - Detects the bounty's world, launches that Story map (configurable Act /
      Difficulty), waits for the run to clear (your units auto-fight), then
      returns to the lobby, claims the reward and accepts the next trait bounty
    - Repeats until there are no trait-reroll bounties left

    DAILY TRAIT FARM:
      Farms every Story/Raid/Challenge map that drops capped Trait Shards.
      Reads your daily cap progress from player data (same X/100 the Play menu
      shows). When a map hits its cap, returns to lobby and moves to the next
      map. Loops through all maps until every daily trait cap is filled.

    AUTO EXECUTE:
      queue_on_teleport re-runs this script after EVERY teleport (manual or
      script-initiated). The queue is kept armed continuously + re-armed on
      OnTeleport so manual lobby/stage hops still resume. Autoexec file (Misc
      tab) is ONLY for full manual rejoins - it skips when a teleport queue
      already fired, preventing double execution.

    ANTI-AFK:
      Blocks the 20-minute idle kick (Idled hook + input nudge + disables any
      built-in AFK script). Toggle it in the Misc tab.

    DPS METER (v1.9.5):
      Live team DPS from leaderstats.Damage + theoretical per-slot DPS (dmg/cd)
      for equipped units. See the DPS tab.

    DAILY TRAIT LEAVE (v1.9.8):
      Leaves the stage as soon as a map's daily Trait Shard cap is full. Tries
      Play/leave, game Play.leave(), Matchmaking/leave, and GUI Leave buttons.

    DAILY TRAIT PRIORITY (v1.11.0):
      Reorder and enable/disable which trait maps to farm. Top of the list is
      farmed first; capped maps are skipped to the next enabled priority map.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------]]

